data.description: Welcome home to 4406 Norfen Rd in Friendship Gardens! Well maintained 3 bed 1.5 baths and spacious walkout basement. The kitchen is equipped with newer appliances and glistening granite counter tops. Many recent updates have been made! HVAC installed end of 2018, Water Heater -2018, Newer Washer and Dryer,  Roof installed 2020, New gutter guards, Kitchen counters 2023, New sump pump 2023, Carpets installed 2023. Primary and half bathroom recently renovated, home fully equipped with conveying security system. Home has a private driveway parking spot which can be accessed through the alley.  You don’t want to miss this opportunity!!
